data.meta_description: We have over 400 diploma, degree, and certificate program offerings to help launch your career. With more accredited programs, pioneering research projects and partnerships that offer semesters or placements abroad. An education rooted in the principles of global citizenship, equity and social inclusion. All at Centennial College.
